1. *Met* je bio potpuno prazan. (The *bucket* was completely empty.)
2. Nisam znao da li da *metem* ulaznu prostoriju ili ne. (I didn't know whether to *sweep* the entrance hall or not.)
3. *Met* je bio smešten u uglu sobe. (The *broom* was placed in the corner of the room.)
4. Kada sam pao, *met* mi je ispao iz ruke. (When I fell, I dropped the *broom* from my hand.)
5. Molim te, da li možeš da *ometeš* svoje razgovore dok učim? (Please, can you *interrupt* your conversations while I'm studying?)
6. Kada je video da sam u nevolji, prišao mi je i *ometnuo* ruku preko ramena. (When he saw that I was in trouble, he approached me and *put* his hand on my shoulder.)
7. Bilo je teško *ometati* se sa velikom krpom na glavi. (It was difficult to *move clumsily* with a big cloth on my head.)
8. *Ometanje* je zakonom zabranjeno. ( *Disturbing* is prohibited by law.)